### ===== AUTH ROUTES =====

### 1. Register new user
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan_petrenko",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Іван"
}

---

### 2. Register duplicate (expect 409)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan_petrenko",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Іван"
}

---

### 3. Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan_petrenko",
  "password": "password123"
}

---

### 4. Login with wrong password (expect 401)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan_petrenko",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

---

### 5. Get profile (replace TOKEN with actual token)
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

---

### 6. Get profile without token (expect 401)
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/me

---

### 7. Refresh token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

---

### 8. Logout (replace TOKEN with actual token)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

---

### ===== ANNOUNCEMENTS ROUTES =====

### 9. Get all announcements (public)
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements

---

### 10. Get one announcement (public)
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements/1

---

### 11. Create announcement (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/announcements
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Продам велосипед",
  "description": "Відмінний велосипед у хорошому стані, мало використовувався",
  "price": 3500
}

---

### 12. Create announcement without token (expect 401)
POST http://localhost:3000/announcements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Продам велосипед",
  "description": "Відмінний велосипед у хорошому стані",
  "price": 3500
}

---

### 13. Update own announcement
PATCH http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 3000
}

---

### 14. Update someone else's announcement (expect 403)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer OTHER_USER_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 1000
}

---

### 15. Delete own announcement
DELETE http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

---

### 16. Delete someone else's announcement (expect 403)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer OTHER_USER_TOKEN_HERE
